Definition: perennial herb native to Europe but naturalized elsewhere having heart-shaped leaves and yellow flowers resembling buttercups
Example: its tuberous roots have been used as a poultice to relieve piles
Synonyms: pilewort, Ranunculus_ficaria, flower, genus_Ranunculus, m, perennial, herb, native, to, Europe, but, naturalized, elsewhere, having, heart-shaped, leaves, and, yellow, flowers, resembling, buttercups, its, tuberous, roots, have, been, used, as, a, poultice, relieve, piles
Category: noun.plant
